title: This John Wick Character has Super Powers! 👊 #shorts
description:
You’ve seen John Wick take out bad guys like it’s nothing, almost like he’s a superhero! But is John Wick 4 actually a superhero movie? Donnie Yen’s character, Caine, definitely makes a GREAT point for this. Sure he’s a blind assassin, and that’s unreal. But what’s most impressive is his ability to read cards. Let us explain…

👀 Mario is IMMORTAL! ►► https://youtu.be/drvPVTMQ8fU
